# Security
- Never commit secrets; load via env (vlucas/phpdotenv or server env).
- Escape output (HTML/JS) and use parameterized queries everywhere.
- Validate and sanitize all input; centralize validation.
- Use password_hash()/password_verify(); never custom crypto.
- Enable SameSite, HttpOnly, Secure cookies; rotate session IDs on login.
